Text: Your Account Transition to NetBankTradingpst Just a reminder that your account will be transitioned from CompuBank to NetBank on Saturday May For important information that you will want to know please go to our Timeline page at compubanktimelinehtm or to our FAQ page at compubankfaqhtm All of us here at NetBank are looking forward to serving your banking needs

Your Transition To NetBankTradingpst Greetings from NetBank This message is to provide you with important information about the transition of your former CompuBank account to NetBank on Saturday May Online Bill Pay The last day to schedule online bill payments is Thursday May Your recurring payments and your payee information will be transferred to NetBank Your payment history will not be transferred to your NetBank account if you want this for your records please print it before Thursday View Only You will be able to view your accounts online at CompuBank on Friday May and until transition on Saturday May Transfers by phone and online will not be possible and balances will not be updated during this transition period Please begin to login to your account directly at on Saturday May and thereafter Please take a moment to go to compubanktimelinehtm for more important information about your new account and its transition to NetBank The page will be updated throughout the weekend If your questions are not answered there please call NetBank Customer Service x at BKONWEB send a message from the Contact Us page on our Web site or after the transition on May send a secure NetBank Bank Mail message after logging into your account We hope May will mark the beginning of a long banking relationship with NetBank
